rComments: Great prof. Exams are fair. She is very clear. The course is not as textbook based as other courses which was awesome! Lectures were very interesting. However, there are only two exams worth 50% each consisting of one midterm and one final.

rComments: The material is straightforward. Pay close attention to the lectures, especially the studies because you need to know that material inside out. Very fair exams.
